Class LinHashMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
      • LinHashMap<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<K,V>

    public class LinHashMap<K,V>
extends java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<K,V>
    This class provides hash maps that use the Linear Hashing algorithm. A hash table is created that is an array of buckets.
    See Also:
